org.hibernate.criterion

Class Subqueries

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.criterion.Subqueries

  • public class Subqueries
extends Object
    Factory class for criterion instances that represent expressions involving subqueries.
    See Also:
    Restrictions, Projection, Criteria
